  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ethical Reflection on Disruptive Technologies and Society: Roundtables on &quot;Ethics of Artificial Intelligence&quot; and &quot;Ethics of Genome Editing&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Policy makers, researchers and the general public especially young people will be sensitized to the ethical implications of AI and genome editing through a series of roundtables involving eminent international experts. Informative and educational videos on these topics will also be produced and widely distributed through UNESCO&apos;s website for educational and awareness raising purposes. Moreover, Private meetings will be held in conjunction with the roundtables where invited international experts, COMEST and IBC members who will explore the ethical issues of genome editing and identify UNESCO&apos;s strategic approach to tackle these issues.</narrative>
  </description>
